    All Classes and Interfaces

    Class
    Description
    Applicant
    Applicant represents a user who can apply for BTO projects.
    ApplicantMenu
    ApplicantMenu provides the user interface for applicant operations.
    ApplicationController
    Handles applicant actions: apply and withdraw.
    ApplicationService
    Implementation of the application service.
    ApplicationStatus
    Represents the possible statuses of a BTO application.
    BTOSystemUser
    BTOSystemUser is an abstract class that extends User and implements ProjectInteractor.
    CLI
    CLI is the main boundary class that handles user interaction.
    Constants
    Constants used throughout the application.
    CSVApplicationRepository
    CSV-based implementation of the application repository.
    CSVEnquiryRepository
    CSV-based implementation of the enquiry repository.
    CSVOfficerRegistrationRepository
    CSV-based implementation of the officer registration repository.
    CSVProjectRepository
    CSV-based implementation of the project repository.
    CSVRepository<T,ID>
    Base class for CSV-based repositories.
    CSVUserRepository
    CSV-based implementation of the user repository.
    Enquiry
    Enquiry represents a query submitted by a user regarding a specific project.
    EnquiryService
    Implementation of the enquiry service.
    FileManager
    Utility class for file operations in the BTO Management System.
    HDBManager
    HDBManager represents an HDB manager, a user who manages project listings.
    HDBManagerMenu
     
    HDBOfficer
    HDBOfficer represents an HDB officer who can manage projects and process applications.
    HDBOfficerMenu
    HDBOfficerMenu is the boundary class for HDB officers.
    IApplicationRepository
    Repository interface for managing applications.
    IApplicationService
    Service interface for application-related operations.
    IEnquiryRepository
    Repository interface for Enquiry entities.
    IEnquiryService
    Service interface for enquiry-related operations.
    InputValidator
    InputValidator contains methods for validating user input such as NRIC, password formats, age requirements, and marital status.
    IOfficerRegistrationRepository
    Repository interface for managing officer registrations.
    IOfficerRegistrationService
    Service interface for officer registration operations.
    IOfficerRegistrationService.OfficerProjectPair
    A simple class to represent an officer-project registration pair.
    IProjectRepository
    Repository interface for Project entities.
    IProjectService
    Service interface for project-related operations.
    IReportService
    Service interface for report generation operations.
    IRepository<T,ID>
    Generic repository interface for CRUD operations.
    IUserRepository
    Repository interface for User entities.
    IUserService
    Service interface for user-related operations.
    IValidationService
    Service interface for validation operations.
    LoginController
    LoginController handles user authentication and password management.
    Main
    Main class that initializes the application.
    OfficerApplicantMenu
    OfficerApplicantMenu provides a UI for officers to use applicant functionalities.
    OfficerAsApplicant
    OfficerAsApplicant is an adapter class that wraps an HDBOfficer instance and presents it as an Applicant.
    OfficerRegistrationService
    Implementation of the officer registration service.
    Project
    Represents a BTO (Build-To-Order) housing project.
    ProjectController
    ProjectController handles operations related to project management such as retrieving project listings, filtering, and toggling project visibility.
    ProjectInteractor
    ProjectInteractor defines common functionality for users who can interact with projects.
    ProjectRepository
     
    ProjectService
    Implementation of the project service.
    ReportController
    ReportController handles the generation of reports for the BTO Management System.
    ReportService
    Implementation of the report service.
    RepositoryFactory
    Factory for creating repository instances.
    ServiceLocator
    A simple service locator implementation for dependency injection.
    User
    User is an abstract base class that defines common attributes for all users.
    UserMenu<T>
    UserMenu is an abstract base class for all user menus.
    UserService
    Implementation of the user service.
    ValidationService
    Implementation of the validation service.
